Package: add2nc
Title: Add Variables and Attributes to Existing NetCDF Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Markus", "Loew", email = "m.loew@unimelb.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides utilities to add timestamp-aligned numeric vectors from a
    data frame into an existing NetCDF file ('add2nc()'), and to add or update
    global metadata attributes ('add_global_nc_attributes()').
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    ncdf4,
    CFtime,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
